flowchart TD
    Internet[Internet]
    CorpFW[Corporate Firewall]
    CorpNet[Corporate IT Network]
    IDMZ[Industrial DMZ]
    OTFW[OT Firewall]
    Switch[Managed Industrial Switch with SPAN Port]

    ENG[ENG-01 Engineering Workstation]
    HMI[HMI-01 HMI Server]
    HIST[HIST-01 Historian]
    PLC1[PLC-01 Siemens PLC]
    PLC2[PLC-02 PLC]

    Zeek[Zeek Monitoring Sensor]
    Logs[Zeek Logs]
    Splunk[Splunk Enterprise]
    SOC[SOC Dashboards & Alerts]

    Internet --> CorpFW --> CorpNet --> IDMZ --> OTFW --> Switch

    Switch --> ENG
    Switch --> HMI
    Switch --> HIST
    Switch --> PLC1
    Switch --> PLC2

    Switch -. mirrored traffic .-> Zeek
    Zeek --> Logs --> Splunk --> SOC
